entries.femaleVariant: A Rostović?! You blind, motherfucker? Techtronika logo's right there!
Got a fight here.
Got a fight here. You Buck?
entries.maleVariant: I got a fight here. You Buck?

entries.femaleVariant: In the flesh.
Heh. Lookin' at you's makin' my wallet wet. Yo, I'm puttin' all I got 'gainst you.
I accept your offer.
Toss in your sniper rifle.
Maybe later.
Nice rifle.
Maybe later.
What, shakin' in your heels? Hah! Ain't no surprise.
entries.maleVariant: What, shakin' in your boots? Hah! Ain't no surprise.

entries.femaleVariant: OK, whatever it takes to shut your mouth.
I don't, no. I'll raise ya instead.
Told ya already... I'm layin' out all I got.
You ready? Not too scared are ya, buttercup?
Like that? You like gettin' yo' ass beat, huh?
God-fuckin'-dammit!
C'mon, hand over the rifle.
Like I thought. Took you for a marshmallow.
Lemme know if you want a rematch. You make a great punchin' bag.
[Start fight] Let's do this.
Hehe. Look forward to it.
This rifle... "Grad," as you said? Where'd ya get it?
Well, well... I see I got a gunthusiast on my hands.
Shhh... Or I'll rip that tongue out.
I take what I deserve.
Somethin' wrong? Baby need a bottle? Take one, even the odds.
The SPT32 "Grad." Best sniper ever made, hands down.
Lil' souvenir from when I served. Why?
Think you're tough shit? Just lucky, that's all...
Very generous. Thanks, Buck.
I tell you to fuck off, or what?
Just curious. Heard that was a limited series. Only three hundred manufactured – KGB-issue.
But we ain't here to talk iron. We here to break bones and crack chrome. So, you accept my offer or not?
Toss in the sniper. That is, unless you're scared...
entries.maleVariant: Toss in the sniper. I mean, that is, unless you're scared...

entries.femaleVariant: Of you? I don't give a fuck 'bout you. Done. Rifle's on the table.
Down to biz, huh? Ain't the only way you're goin' down.
Follow me.
Over my rottin' meat. Get her!
entries.maleVariant: Over my rottin' meat. Get him!

entries.femaleVariant: Uh-huh, whatever you say. I'll take my eddies now.
Take 'em and fuck off.
If you tryna piss me off, you doin' a hella good job.
That's right, I am.
Relax. Just a sport.
Ugh, relax, Buck. Just some friendly competition.
entries.maleVariant: Relax, Buck. It's just some friendly competition.

entries.femaleVariant: Fuck you. Fuck your friendly competition.
I've just been wondering why you need such a long, looong rifle?
Fuck you mean?
Seems like you're overcompensating for somethin'... A certain shortcoming, if you will.
Buck, I'm sayin' you got the microdick of a field mouse.
Oh, you're a fuckin' corpse!
Hm, no lack in confidence, I see.
An' I'll show you why. This arm's military issue. Titanium bones, carbon fiber. Could punch a hole through a tank if I wanted.
So? We got a deal? Or's that piss I smell drippin' down your leg?
